{
  "stem": "2004.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we-- of course, we got into Germany-- unofficially, but we got there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now we were in Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the next stop, we have to find the DP camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We found out that there's a nearby DP camp in Austria.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I ended up in Fernwald.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was in Fernwald from early 1946, which must've been around February 1946 until-- and then, of course, as soon as I had a chance, I registered with the American consulate to immigrate to the United States, which made it a little easier because I came under a certain youth quota.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was through the auspices of the actually American Joint Distribution Committee, which is an arm of the HIAS.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in 1947, which was about a little over a year later, I landed in New York in June 22, 1947.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did not have-- I-- we-- before we got on the boat, we got $15, $10 or $15, which was Coke money.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So I arrived in the United States with $15 in my pocket, OK?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were put up on-- in Manhattan on 103rd Street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a hotel called the Marseilles Hotel, which was specifically reserved for us young people that just arrived.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were other guests there too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the, the HIAS reserved some room for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they gave us rooms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had rooms there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, you know, in the evening, I'm standing in front of that hotel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And comes across a, a, a man and a lady.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they say, does any one of you know somebody by the name of Max Durst?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, I am Max Durst.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're Max Durst?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My name is Jack Manash.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is my wife Sally Manash.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, you're Jack Manash?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
